  </script><div class="top-advert-sas"></div><div class="StoryTplImgOnly-contentMeta"><div class="tablet-landscape-none"><div class="StoryTooltip StoryTooltip--withDarkLine"><aside><a href="https://www.ozy.com/news-and-politics/" class="apply-bgcolor"><span>News + Politics</span></a></aside></div></div><div class="StoryTplImgOnly-title mobile-block tablet-landscape-none"><h1>Chapter Two of Trump&#8217;s Presidency: The Next 100 Days</h1></div><div class="tablet-landscape-none"><div class="StorySocial"><ul><li><a title="Share to Facebook" data-addthis-url="https://www.ozy.com/news-and-politics/chapter-two-of-trumps-presidency-the-next-100-days/77048/" data-addthis-title="Chapter Two of Trump’s Presidency: The Next 100 Days" data-addthis-description="As Donald Trump’s first 100 days in the White House come to a close, OZY looks ahead at the people and policies to watch from Day 101 to 200." data-evcat="Story Page" data-evact="top-share-block" data-evlabel="FB Share" class="Link addthis_button_facebook facebook-share" href="#"><span class="Icon Icon--facebook Icon--abs"> </span><span class="AssistiveText">Facebook</span></a></li><li><a title="Share to Twitter" data-addthis-url="https://www.ozy.com/news-and-politics/chapter-two-of-trumps-presidency-the-next-100-days/77048/" data-addthis-title="Chapter Two of Trump’s Presidency: The Next 100 Days" data-addthis-description="As Donald Trump’s first 100 days in the White House come to a close, OZY looks ahead at the people and policies to watch from Day 101 to 200." data-evcat="Story Page" data-evact="top-share-block" data-evlabel="TW Share" class="Link addthis_button_twitter twitter-share" href="#"><span class="Icon Icon--twitter Icon--abs"> </span><span class="AssistiveText">Twitter</span></a></li><li class="StorySocial-shareLoveThis apply-color"><span>Love this?<span>share</span></span></li><li><a href="mailto:?subject=Chapter Two of Trump’s Presidency: The Next 100 Days&amp;body=As Donald Trump’s first 100 days in the W