senators in supporting Trump, and Yahoo! News recently reported\u0026nbsp;growing frustration among the committee’s Democrats that Burr is slow-walking the probe. If it\u0026nbsp;appears to be tainted by politics, pressure will grow for a special prosecutor to come in. Ask Ken Starr and Bill Clinton how that works out.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003ch4 id=\"When_trade_bluster_meets_policy\"\u003eWhen trade bluster meets policy\u003cstrong\u003e\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/h4\u003e\n\u003cdiv class=\"inline_image inline_image_left image_size_med fullsize inline-element\" data-attachment=\"106604\" data-sequence=\"4\" id=\"168100\" inline-image=\"\"\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003ca class=\"hash-link\" id=\"img168100\"\u003e \u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cdiv class=\"picture\"\u003e\u003cimg alt=\"china shipping containers\" src=\"https://www.ozy.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/v-s-k-shutterstock_189076856.jpg?w=660\" data-image-tablet=\"https://www.ozy.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/v-s-k-shutterstock_189076856.jpg?w=768\" data-image-tablet-size=\"768xany\" data-image-large=\"https://www.ozy.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/v-s-k-shutterstock_189076856.jpg?w=940\" data-image-large-size=\"940xany\"\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\n\u003cdiv class=\"sharing-options\"\u003e\n\u003cdiv class=\"close-button\" close-button-share=\"\"\u003e\u003cspan class=\"ozy-icon i-share-icon i-share-icon-dims\"\u003e\u0026nbsp;\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\n\u003cdiv class=\"share-item\" url=\"https://www.ozy.com/politics-and-power/chapter-two-of-trumps-presidency-the-next-100-days/77048/#img168100\" picture=\"https://www.ozy.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/v-s-k-shutterstock_189076856.jpg?w=660\" title=\"Chapter Two of Trump's Presidency: The Next 100 Days\" description=\"As Donald Trump’s first 100 days in the White House come to a close, OZY looks ahead at the people and policies to watch from Day 101 to 200.\"\u003e\u003ca class=\"facebook-share\" facebook-picture-share=\"\" href=\"javascript:void(0)\" da